-- Putin Wants Positive Approach to Cyprus Loan Bid, Politis Says
-- B y   S t e l i o s   O r p h a n i d e s
-- 2012-06-28T11:33:31Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-28/putin-wants-positive-approach-to-cyprus-loan-bid-politis-says.html
President  Vladimir Putin  instructed
the Russian Finance Ministry to take a positive approach to a
request from Cyprus for a loan of 5 billion euros ($6.2
billion),  Politis  reported.  The Russian leader also told the ministry to review
Cyprus’s request as soon as possible, the Nicosia-based
newspaper reported today without saying where it got the
information.  Putin’s spokesman,  Dmitry Peskov , declined to comment on
the report when contacted by Bloomberg News.  Click here for Web link   To contact the reporters on this story:
